.TH AADK-UI 1 "April 2026" "AADK" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
aadk-ui \- GTK4 client for the Android DevKit workflow suite
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B aadk-ui
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B aadk-ui
opens the graphical AADK client for project, toolchain, target, workflow, and
evidence management.
.PP
The UI expects the AADK gRPC services to be available on the configured local
addresses. The packaged
.BR aadk (1)
launcher starts those services automatically before opening the UI.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/aadk/state/ui-config.json
Persisted UI configuration.
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/aadk/state/ui-state.json
Persisted UI state.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR aadk (1),
.BR aadk-cli (1)
